[*] --> Processing
Processing --> Closed : review
Closed --> Pending : review
Closed : entry / log library
Pending --> Rejected : confirm
Rejected --> Active : approve
Rejected : entry / log library
Active --> OnHold : confirm
OnHold --> [*]
@enduml